Build & Run Instructions

Requirements:
Visual Studio Build Tools 2022 (MSVC)
CMake 3.21+
vcpkg installed and integrated with Visual Studio


# Clone repository
git clone https://github.com/<your-username>/gravity-sim.git
cd gravity-sim

# Configure
cmake -S . -B build -G "Visual Studio 17 2022" -A x64

# Build
cmake --build build --config Release

# Run
build\Release\gravity_sim.exe


